Number 10 also confirmed that there would be a summit press conference.

‘There will be an opportunity to ask questions,’ the spokesman said.

French journalists were widely criticised for their failure to grill Mr Hollande about his affair when he gave a press conference in Paris days after details of his trysts emerged.

